Package: goatHapNet
Type: Package
Title: Automated Haplotype Network Plots from Regional Goat VCF Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yefang", "Li", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "your.email@example.com")
  )
Description: Extracts a gene or candidate interval from a VCF, phases it with
    Beagle, builds haplotypes, calculates sample-group frequencies, and exports
    publication-ready haplotype network plots as PDF, SVG, and TIFF.
